				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$u_\gamma \left( {\gamma _c} \right) = \frac{{\left| {\gamma _c - \gamma _t} \right|}}{{\left| {\gamma _w - \gamma _t} \right|}}$$\end{document}where uγ(γc) is the dissatisfaction factor, γc is the current possible outcome, γt is the target outcome, and γw is the worst outcome.
